title: Death Row - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/21/22
itunes:title: Death Row - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/21/22
description:
George Noory and podcaster Corny Koehl discuss the wrongful conviction of Jarvis Jay Masters, sentenced to death for his alleged role in the murder of a prison guard while he was serving time for another crime, and how his case changed her views on the death penalty.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
